name: Sonic Chicken
text:
1 "Sonic" Tuner Monster + 1 or more non-Tuner Monsters
If this card is Synchro Summoned you can return cards your opponent controls to the hand, up to the number of your banished "Sonic" monsters with different names. If this card was Synchro Summoned using "Sonic Duck" as a Synchro Material, your opponent cannot activate cards or effects in response to this effect.
